# Orinax CRM — Core Rules

## Server Isolation (CRITICAL)

The server at `188.225.86.66` hosts multiple projects. You MUST:

- **ONLY** work inside `/root/orinax-crm/` on the server — NEVER touch any other directory
- **NEVER** modify `/root/crm-app/`, `/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/crm-app`, or any other existing project files
- **NEVER** restart services that belong to other projects (e.g., PM2 processes not named `orinax-crm`)
- Before any server command, verify it targets `/root/orinax-crm/` or `crm.orinax.ai` configs only

## After Every Code Change

After every meaningful code change, you MUST:

1. `git add . && git commit -m "..."` — commit to GitHub repo `orinax-crm`
2. `git push origin main`
3. SSH into server and run deploy: `cd /root/orinax-crm && git pull && npm install && npm run build && pm2 restart orinax-crm`

Never skip this. Code changes without commit + deploy are incomplete.

